attributes.name: world
attributes.value: Kepler-22b. The promised second Earth six hundred light-years from home.

attributes.name: culture
attributes.value: Hybrid. This society dwells in structures that, although capable of flying, are usually attached to the ground.

attributes.name: community size
attributes.value: A small, possibly young colony resembling a town.

attributes.name: festive colors
attributes.value: Golden shades that represent the grandeur of a now de-grown civilization.
